Method Detail

setConfig

public void setConfig(XmlElement xml)
Deprecated. 
Configures the Encryption filter for password based encryption.

Supported configuration elements include:

  • password - (required) the raw material used to generate the secret key
  • salt - the salt to use in deriving the key
  • iterations - the iteration count to use in deriving the key
  • algorithm - the mechanism to use in deriving a secret key from the above material

Specified by:
setConfig in interface XmlConfigurable

setConfig in class SymmetricEncryptionFilter
